### Quiz System API 测试集合
### 使用 REST Client 扩展或类似工具执行

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### ==================== 健康检查 ====================

### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ==================== 科目管理 ====================

### 2. 获取所有科目
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams

### 3. 按分类获取科目
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams?category=英语

### 4. 获取单个科目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams/{{examId}}

### 5. 创建科目（管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/exams/admin
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "教育心理学复习题库",
  "category": "专业课",
  "icon": "/uploads/edu-psych.png",
  "description": "教师资格证考试必备题库",
  "sortOrder": 10
}

### 6. 切换科目启用状态（管理员）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/exams/admin/{{examId}}/toggle

### ==================== 激活码管理 ====================

### 7. 生成激活码（管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/codes/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "examId": "{{examId}}",
  "count": 10,
  "source": "XHS",
  "note": "小红书活动赠送"
}

### 8. 查询激活码列表（管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/codes?examId={{examId}}&isUsed=false

### 9. 激活码核销（用户）
POST {{baseUrl}}/activate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "ABC12345",
  "userId": "wx_openid_123456"
}

### 10. 检查用户权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/permissions/check?userId=wx_openid_123456&examId={{examId}}

### 11. 获取用户的所有权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/permissions/wx_openid_123456

### ==================== 题目管理 ====================

### 12. 获取题目列表（不含答案）
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/{{examId}}?userId=wx_openid_123456

### 13. 按题型筛选题目
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/{{examId}}?type=SINGLE&userId=wx_openid_123456

### 14. 获取单题详情（含答案）
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/{{examId}}/{{questionId}}?userId=wx_openid_123456

### 15. 创建题目（管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions/admin
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "examId": "{{examId}}",
  "type": "SINGLE",
  "content": "教育的本质是什么？",
  "options": [
    { "key": "A", "value": "培养人" },
    { "key": "B", "value": "传授知识" },
    { "key": "C", "value": "发展智力" },
    { "key": "D", "value": "塑造品格" }
  ],
  "answer": "A",
  "explanation": "教育是一种培养人的社会活动，这是教育的本质属性。",
  "difficulty": 2,
  "tags": ["教育学", "基础概念"]
}

### 16. 批量导入题目（管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions/admin/import
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "examId": "{{examId}}",
  "questions": [
    {
      "type": "SINGLE",
      "content": "教学过程的本质是什么？",
      "options": [
        { "key": "A", "value": "认识过程" },
        { "key": "B", "value": "实践活动" }
      ],
      "answer": "A",
      "explanation": "教学过程本质上是一种认识过程"
    },
    {
      "type": "MULTI",
      "content": "以下哪些属于教学原则？",
      "options": [
        { "key": "A", "value": "科学性与教育性相结合" },
        { "key": "B", "value": "理论联系实际" },
        { "key": "C", "value": "因材施教" },
        { "key": "D", "value": "死记硬背" }
      ],
      "answer": ["A", "B", "C"],
      "explanation": "ABC都是教学原则，D不是"
    },
    {
      "type": "JUDGE",
      "content": "教育是人类特有的社会现象。",
      "options": [
        { "key": "A", "value": "正确" },
        { "key": "B", "value": "错误" }
      ],
      "answer": "A",
      "explanation": "教育是人类所特有的有意识的社会活动"
    }
  ]
}

### 17. 更新题目（管理员）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/questions/admin/{{questionId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "更新后的题目内容",
  "explanation": "更新后的解析"
}

### 18. 删除题目（管理员）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/questions/admin/{{questionId}}
